  "encoding": "windows-1252",
  "html": "\n<div><center>\n<table bordercolor=\"#000080\">\n<tr>\n<td><font><img src=\"../images/R.gif\"/> <strong>all the\n        day</strong></font><hr noshade=\"\"/>\n<p><font>Perhaps an ironic reference to Spenser,\n        <em>Faerie Queene</em>: \"All night she spent in\n        bidding of her bedes, / And all the day in doing good and\n        godly deedes.\" - Volupine has been with Burbank all\n        night and vainly displays her in her shuttered barge all\n        day, trying to impress him (like Cleopatra).</font></p>\n<p><font><em>reference topics</em></font></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td>Volupine and \"Cleopatra\"</td>\n<td><a href=\"Stonesi_JR.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>Structural analysis</td>\n<td><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><font>back to \"Burbank\"</font></a></td>\n<td><a href=\"Burbank_A.htm\"><img src=\"../images/arrowry.gif\"/></a></td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n</center></div>\n",
  "text": "all the day Perhaps an ironic reference to Spenser, Faerie Queene : \"All night she spent in bidding of her bedes, / And all the day in doing good and godly deedes.\" - Volupine has been with Burbank all night and vainly displays her in her shuttered barge all day, trying to impress him (like Cleopatra). reference topics Volupine and \"Cleopatra\" Structural analysis back to \"Burbank\"",
